Wedding Planning Services

Creating Memorable Moments, Crafting Timeless Weddings

Our Wedding Planning Services

Every wedding is a beautiful story, and we believe it deserves to be told with love, care, and attention to detail. At WedSymphony, our expert wedding planners bring years of experience and cultural expertise to ensure your special day is nothing short of magical.

What We Offer:

  • Initial Consultation: Understanding your vision and preferences.
  • Venue Selection: Finding the perfect venue that aligns with your theme.
  • Vendor Coordination: Handpicking the best vendors for your wedding.
  • Guest List Management: Ensuring everyone is invited and well taken care of.
  • Budget Planning: Keeping your wedding within your desired budget.
  • Catering Coordination: Offering a variety of traditional and contemporary Indian cuisine.
  • Decoration: Bringing the cultural beauty of Indian weddings to life with exquisite décor.
  • Timeline Management: Making sure everything runs smoothly from the start to the end of your celebration.
  • And much more! Let us take the stress out of wedding planning so you can focus on enjoying your day.

Our Wedding Planning Packages

Our wedding planning packages are designed to fit every budget and ensure the highest level of service. Whether you want an intimate ceremony or a grand celebration, we’ve got you covered.

Basic Package

Let Us Make Your Wedding a Masterpiece

Get in touch with us to start planning your dream wedding today. Our team is excited to work with you every step of the way.
